column2: >Have Fun With Other Drivers While On The Road

column1: No more road rage! The SquareBlock™ allows you to display whatever you want on your car window! You'll sure get a laugh out of other drivers.
1) Plug in cord that comes with the package into the screen.
2) Connect it to your car's auxilary power outlet (also known as a car cigarette lighter).
3) Download the app (which is included in the intructions manual) to display whatever you want on the screen
One SquareBlock™ with suctions, a five meters special power adapter (long enough to connect the device from the back to the front of your car), and a product intructions manual.

We love our SquareBlock™ and are confident you will too! Our customers are our most important priority that's why we're offering a 30-Day, Money Back Gaurantee. If you're not in love with it, we'll give a full refund.
